              All That I Could / It's You

description:
Silky 2-step soul and Todd Edwards-styled speed garage from the UK garage don, DJ Q

‘All That I Could’ is a twinkle-toed beaut dripping with deep keys and sweetest cut-up vocals nodding to the OG Todd Edwards in a swinging UKG 2-step, before he shifts the gears into four-to-da-floor Todd Da God vibes on ‘’It’s You’.
